{"tid":2425141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"接連有亞裔員工遇襲 紐約連鎖中菜館提早收工","createTime":"2021-02-27T06:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T07:57:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"976cbc6e87eb4571110255afba021a1f70ae5e95","tid":2425141,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"紐約巿連鎖中菜餐廳「西安名吃」（Xi&rsquo;an Famous Foods）表示，餐廳在兩至三個月內，先後有兩名亞裔員工遇襲，為確保員工安全，決定縮短營業時間，讓員工早點回家。<br />\n<br />\n現年33歲的王夢迪（Janson Wang）是「西安名吃」的行政總裁，他接受作家范伯格（Shaina Feinberg）和插畫家羅斯曼（Julia Rothman）訪問，講述旗下餐廳在疫情下的遭遇和難關，文章和插畫刊登於《紐約時報》。<br />\n<br />\n王夢迪表示他和父親來自西安，其後全家移民來美，曾在康涅狄格州生活，每日面對種族歧視問題，到他高中時才全家搬到紐約市，「紐約市是我們的避風港，我很期望來到這裏，在這裏我有歸屬感。」<br />\n<br />\n王夢迪的爸爸過去一直在中餐館工作，其後自立門戶，在法拉盛黃金商場（Golden Mall） 開設首間「西安名吃」，不再做美式中餐，只賣自己喜歡的中國菜。王夢迪大學畢業後，於2009年投入家族生意，把「西安名吃」慢慢發展成連鎖餐廳，「我們現在有8間門市，我們曾經有14間分店，但有6間在疫情下已經倒閉了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210227/6ZFNLPFR7ZHMRHIL44R4VUQXRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210227%2F6ZFNLPFR7ZHMRHIL44R4VUQXRM%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=93ff2937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210227%2F6ZFNLPFR7ZHMRHIL44R4VUQXRM%2F&h=fedd87b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210227/6ZFNLPFR7ZHMRHIL44R4VUQXRM/</a>"},{"pid":"0a3ed46a07ad5a9e08e42427e6a39049909c14a0","tid":2425141,"uid":70439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f979845171a5434c005048f1b5f85ffa631ccb60","tid":2425141,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.g