:10:50.000Z","msg":"韓國移民識做rooftop Koreans<br />\n華僑唔識搵嘢傍身？"},{"pid":"c622acdd6cf576f7029e2f912503dbf4028141d3","tid":2425141,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">王夢迪表示他和父親來自西安</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d524b760b9934141167049ea1a475ed24d48b99","tid":2425141,"uid":124350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"整場yellow lives matter啦<br />\n<br />\n不過虛偽美國左膠應該唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}